      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It's crucial to be transparent while maintaining a carefully managed narrative. Instead of the loaded term \"breach,\" you might frame it as an \"unauthorized data exposure\" or a \"security misconfiguration.\" The statement should immediately emphasize that the compromised data was limited to non-sensitive user email addresses, and that immediate remedial actions have been taken to prevent recurrence. This approach shows accountability without triggering the worst-case public panic.",
